      "recording_attendee_id": "a9707d21-0368-4805-be87-7260c94787df",
      "order_number": 4,
      "text": "Still connecting the audio, Steven."
    },
    {
      "id": "5817f1ed-31d0-4727-b0c5-2e2acfd21958",
      "recording_id": "95d0d360-662d-4647-a851-472b33b81a92",
      "end_time": 43.26,
      "start_time": 40.46,
      "recording_attendee_id": "a9707d21-0368-4805-be87-7260c94787df",
      "order_number": 5,
      "text": "I'm not able to hear you though."
    },
    {
      "id": "5817f1ed-31d0-4727-b0c5-2e2acfd21958",
      "recording_id": "95d0d360-662d-4647-a851-472b33b81a92",
      "end_time": 44.52,
      "start_time": 43.76,
      "recording_attendee_id": "a9707d21-0368-4805-be87-7260c94787df",
      "order_number": 6,
      "text": "Um,"
    },
    {
      "id": "5817f1ed-31d0-4727-b0c5-2e2acfd21958",
      "recording_id": "95d0d360-662d-4647-a851-472b33b81a92",
      "end_time": 48.66,
      "start_time": 47.08,
      "recording_attendee_id": "a9707d21-0368-4805-be87-7260c94787df",
      "order_number": 7,
      "text": "doesn't say you're muted but"
    },
    {
      "id": "5817f1ed-31d0-4727-b0c5-2e2acfd21958",
      "recording_id": "95d0d360-662d-4647-a851-472b33b81a92",
      "end_time": 56.83,
      "start_time": 56.79,
      "recording_attendee_id": "a9707d21-0368-4805-be87-7260c94787df",
      "order_number": 8,
      "text": "yeah,"
    },
    {
      "id": "5817f1ed-31d0-4727-b0c5-2e2acfd21958",
      "recording_id": "95d0d360-662d-4647-a851-472b33b81a92",
      "end_time": 78.38,
      "start_time": 72.58,
      "recording_attendee_id": "a9707d21-0368-4805-be87-7260c94787df",
      "order_number": 9,
      "text": "but he've, he was here then he kind of hear him and he, uh, he hopped out."
    },
    {
      "id": "5817f1ed-31d0-4727-b0c5-2e2acfd21958",
      "recording_id": "95d0d360-662d-4647-a851-472b33b81a92",
      "end_time": 81.39,
      "start_time": 79.01,
      "recording_attendee_id": "a9707d21-0368-4805-be87-7260c94787df",
      "order_number": 10,
      "text": "It's crazy how many issues people were having, man."
    },
    {
      "id": "5817f1ed-31d0-4727-b0c5-2e2acfd21958",
      "recording_id": "95d0d360-662d-4647-a851-472b33b81a92",
      "end_time": 86.31,
      "start_time": 81.79,
      "recording_attendee_id": "a9707d21-0368-4805-be87-7260c94787df",
      "order_number": 11,
      "text": "I think the audio issue has to do with, um, like our recorder, the sales loft recorder."
    },
    {
      "id": "5817f1ed-31d0-4727-b0c5-2e2acfd21958",
      "recording_id": "95d0d360-662d-4647-a851-472b33b81a92",
      "end_time": 88.78,
      "start_time": 87.61,
      "recording_attendee_id": "a9707d21-0368-4805-be87-7260c94787df",
      "order_number": 12,
      "text": "Oh, you think so?"
    },
    {
      "id": "5817f1ed-31d0-4727-b0c5-2e2acfd21958",
      "recording_id": "95d0d360-662d-4647-a851-472b33b81a92",
      "end_time": 89.82,
      "start_time": 88.79,
      "recording_attendee_id": "a9707d21-0368-4805-be87-7260c94787df",
      "order_number": 13,
      "text": "Should I not record?"
    },
    {
      "id": "5817f1ed-31d0-4727-b0c5-2e2acfd21958",
      "recording_id": "95d0d360-662d-4647-a851-472b33b81a92",
      "end_time": 92.85,
      "start_time": 90.89,
      "recording_attendee_id": "a9707d21-0368-4805-be87-7260c94787df",
      "order_number": 14,
      "text": "Um, no, I mean, it's fine."
    },
    {
      "id": "5817f1ed-31d0-4727-b0c5-2e2acfd21958",
      "recording_id": "95d0d360-662d-4647-a851-472b33b81a92",
      "end_time": 96.21,
      "start_time": 92.86,
      "recording_attendee_id": "a9707d21-0368-4805-be87-7260c94787df",
      "order_number": 15,
      "text": "It's probably fine, but that's something that someone was telling me the other day and it kind of makes a little bit of sense."
    },
    {
      "id": "5817f1ed-31d0-4727-b0c5-2e2acfd21958",
      "recording_id": "95d0d360-662d-4647-a851-472b33b81a92",
      "end_time": 97.47,
      "start_time": 96.22,
      "recording_attendee_id": "a9707d21-0368-4805-be87-7260c94787df",
      "order_number": 16,
      "text": "So, yeah."
    },
    {
      "id": "5817f1ed-31d0-4727-b0c5-2e2acfd21958",
      "recording_id": "95d0d360-662d-4647-a851-472b33b81a92",
      "end_time": 100.48,
      "start_time": 97.48,
      "recording_attendee_id": "a9707d21-0368-4805-be87-7260c94787df",
      "order_number": 17,
      "text": "Yeah, nothing like this was happening before."
    },
    {
      "id": "5817f1ed-31d0-4727-b0c5-2e2acfd21958",
      "recording_id": "95d0d360-662d-4647-a851-472b33b81a92",
      "end_time": 104.88,
      "start_time": 100.49,
      "recording_attendee_id": "a9707d21-0368-4805-be87-7260c94787df",
      "order_number": 18,
      "text": "Um, yeah, it seems that there's more mic issues lately now than ever and gone."
    },
    {
      "id": "5817f1ed-31d0-4727-b0c5-2e2acfd21958",
      "recording_id": "95d0d360-662d-4647-a851-472b33b81a92",
      "end_time": 105.22,
      "start_time": 105.03,
      "recording_attendee_id": "a9707d21-0368-4805-be87-7260c94787df",
      "order_number": 19,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "id": "5817f1ed-31d0-4727-b0c5-2e2acfd21958",
      "recording_id": "95d0d360-662d-4647-a851-472b33b81a92",
      "end_time": 108.55,
      "start_time": 105.89,
      "recording_attendee_id": "a9707d21-0368-4805-be87-7260c94787df",
      "order_number": 20,
      "text": "Hey, Steven, are you able to hear us, man?"
    },
    {
      "id": "5817f1ed-31d0-4727-b0c5-2e2acfd21958",
      "recording_id": "95d0d360-662d-4647-a851-472b33b81a92",
      "end_time": 129.47,
      "start_time": 128.57,
      "recording_attendee_id": "a9707d21-0368-4805-be87-7260c94787df",
      "order_number": 21,
      "text": "All righty."
    },
    {
      "id": "5817f1ed-31d0-4727-b0c5-2e2acfd21958",
      "recording_id": "95d0d360-662d-4647-a851-472b33b81a92",
      "end_time": 132.54,
      "start_time": 131.45,
      "recording_attendee_id": "a9707d21-0368-4805-be87-7260c94787df",
      "order_number": 22,
      "text": "Blink once."
